## Introduction


In alignment with the Forgotten Formula PMA's mission of prioritizing healing over profits, this document outlines the process for optimizing the user interface and user experience of highly trafficked files within our platform. This task is crucial for enhancing member engagement and improving the overall usability of our digital health solutions.


## Objective


The primary goal of this task is to identify and propose UI/UX enhancements for our core web pages, ensuring they reflect modern design principles while supporting the PMA's holistic healing approach. These improvements should prioritize user-friendly interactions, aesthetic appeal, and align with our healing mission.


## Target Files


