## UI/UX Improvement Focus Areas


- **Aesthetic Enhancements**: Improve the visual appeal through color schemes, typography, and layout adjustments that resonate with our brand standards.
- **Interactive Flows**: Enhance the intuitiveness and interactivity of user flows, ensuring seamless navigation and increased user satisfaction.
- **Modern Design Principles**: Integrate current design trends that emphasize accessibility, responsiveness, and minimalism, while maintaining alignment with our healing philosophy.


